'''袋獾面部腫瘤病'''（{{lang-en|Devil facial tumour disease, DFTD}}）是感染[[袋獾|袋獾]]的一种非病毒性传染性{{link-en|寄生性肿瘤|parasitic cancer}}<ref>{{cite news |author= |coauthors= |title=Findings on Origin of a Cancer in Tasmanian Devils |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2010/01/01/science/01devil.html |quote=The Tasmanian devil, the spaniel-size marsupial found on the Australian island of Tasmania, has been hurtling toward extinction in recent years, the victim of a bizarre and mysterious facial cancer that spreads like a plague. |work=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]] |date=December 31, 2009 |accessdate=2009-12-31 |archive-date=2019-09-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190907121539/https://www.nytimes.com/2010/01/01/science/01devil.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。该疾病的第一个“官方案例”于1996年出现在澳大利亚。在接下来的10年中，这一疾病使[[塔斯馬尼亞州|塔斯馬尼亞州]]的野生袋獾数量大大减少，估计袋獾群体数量减少20%至50%，遍布占全州65%的范围<ref name="dftdupdatejune20005">DPIWE. 2005. [http://www.dpiwe.tas.gov.au/inter.nsf/Attachments/LBUN-6D73V5/$FILE/Tas_devil_update_June2005.pdf Devil Facial Tumour Disease – Update June 2005] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dpiwe.tas.gov.au/inter.nsf/Attachments/LBUN-6D73V5/$FILE/Tas_devil_update_June2005.pdf |date=20080907075720 }}</ref><ref name="dpiwe dms2005">DPIWE. 2005. [http://www.dpiwe.tas.gov.au/inter.nsf/Attachments/LBUN-6996MH/$FILE/DFTD_DMS_Feb05a.pdf Tasmanian Devil Facial Tumor Disease, Disease Management Strategy] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dpiwe.tas.gov.au/inter.nsf/Attachments/LBUN-6996MH/$FILE/DFTD_DMS_Feb05a.pdf |date=20080907075712 }}</ref>。被感染的群体在12-18个月内的死亡率达100％<ref name="dpiweweb3">DPIWE. [http://www.dpiwe.tas.gov.au/inter.nsf/WebPages/LBUN-5QF86G?open Disease Affecting Tasmanian Devils] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dpiwe.tas.gov.au/inter.nsf/WebPages/LBUN-5QF86G?open |date=20050921014142 }}</ref>。这一疾病主要集中在塔斯馬尼亞州的东半部。

袋獾面部腫瘤病从口部开始出现表观[[病变|病变]]及肿块。这些变化从面部传播到全身并发展成为肿瘤。这些肿瘤影响采食并导致受感染的动物饥饿死亡。

[[传染性肿瘤|传染性肿瘤]]极其罕见。其它已知的类型为{{link-en|犬传染性性病瘤|canine transmissible venereal tumor}}。犬传染性性病瘤通过狗的性行为传播<ref>Loh, Richmond. 2003. Tasmanian Devil (Sarcophilus harrisii) facial tumour (DFT). Paper prepared for the Devil Facial Tumour Disease Workshop, Sir Raymond Ferrall Centre, University of Tasmania, Newnham, 14 October 2003, p. 2.</ref><ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/asia-pacific/6378279.stm Experts tackle the devil's tumour] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/asia-pacific/6378279.stm |date=20181028023559 }}, ''[[BBC_News|BBC News]]'', 20 February 2007.</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Study Finds That a Type of Cancer in Dogs Is Contagious |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/08/10/AR2006081001535.html |work=The Washington Post |date=11 August 2006 |accessdate=11 August 2006 |archive-date=2019-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190214091148/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/08/10/AR2006081001535.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===病理===

生長很大的腫瘤會妨礙覓食，因飢餓而死亡是常見原因。器官受累以及另外的感染也可能是在死亡的另一個因素，常見區域性淋巴結受累及全身轉移。癌症可侵入心臟。

腫瘤是能夠溶解顱骨的一部分。

腫瘤是“大而堅實，軟組織腫塊通常扁平，中央潰爛，表面滲出體液”，這是“典型的多中心，首先出現在口腔，面部，頸部地區”。腫瘤是由外接“以輪式浸潤性結節聚集，以梭形細胞，常在假包膜，並通過細膩的纖維分為小葉。”

